al\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ckt1665702791811.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ckt1665702791811.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ckt1665702791811.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ckt1665702791811\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Entity Interface\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this form to define the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Interface</span> property of and entity, which defines its physical characteristics of in the database.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__p_d5228e1_d5229e1_d5230e1\">It is only necessary to define your own entity interfaces if you want to change the defaults, such the size, character set, and included entities. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a> .</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__p_d5231e1_d5232e1_d5233e1\">If you have created modeled database interface definitions, click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Use modeled</span> to select the one you want to use. This is useful when you want to use the same layout for multiple fields.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__section_ukm_lys_lcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1079399e77\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__ul_qgx_mys_lcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2237e1_d2238e1_d2239e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2240e1_d2241e1_d2242e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2243e1_d2244e1_d2245e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"udr1665702710295.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udr1665702710295.html\" title=\"Character set used for storing the entity in the database.\">Character Set</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2246e1_d2247e1_d2248e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"blo1665702710364.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blo1665702710364.html\" title=\"Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code. If the database does not support Unicode, or it supports only Unicode BMP, use this setting to change its behavior. Valid values are Unicode, BMP, or Use Character Set.\">Wide Character Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2249e1_d2250e1_d2251e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcw1665702710436.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcw1665702710436.html\" title=\"Method used to identify the beginning of an included entities and occurrences using variable length techniques.\">Identification Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2252e1_d2253e1_d2254e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhg1665702710574.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhg1665702710574.html\" title=\"ASCII string that marks the beginning of an included entity.\">Entity Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2255e1_d2256e1_d2257e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"opw1665702710725.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/opw1665702710725.html\" title=\"ASCII string that marks the beginning of the first occurrence of an included entity.\">First Occurrence Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2258e1_d2259e1_d2260e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xaa1665702710795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xaa1665702710795.html\" title=\"ASCII string that marks the beginning of all subsequent occurrences of an included entity when using variable-length techniques.\">Next Occurrence Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2261e1_d2262e1_d2263e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"guc1665702710864.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/guc1665702710864.html\" title=\"Physical size of the entity or included entity, in characters.\">Fixed Length of Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2264e1_d2265e1_d2266e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fwr1665702710934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fwr1665702710934.html\" title=\"Number of characters allocated to each occurrence of the entity.\">Fixed Length of Occurrence</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ckt1665702791811__li_d2267e1_d2268e1_d2269e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfy1703055298366.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Entities</a><p>A Modeled Entity is a main development object that represents a logical data aggregation such as a database table,a collection of records, user interface controls, or other data structure. It is an abstract object that is intended for re-use in other objects, such as components, variables, and parameters.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Entity Interface Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Entity Interface Use this form to define the Database Interface property of and entity, which defines its physical characteristics of in the database. It is only necessary to define your own entity interfaces if you want to change the defaults, such the size, character set, and included entities. For more information, see Database Interface (Entities) . If you have created modeled database interface definitions, click Use modeled to select the one you want to use. This is useful when you want to use the same layout for multiple fields. Properties Name Description Character Set Wide Character Behavior Identification Type Entity Identifier First Occurrence Identifier Next Occurrence Identifier Fixed Length of Entity Fixed Length of Occurrence Comments Related Links Modeled Entities A Modeled Entity is a main development object that represents a logical data aggregation such as a database table,a collection of records, user interface controls, or other data structure. It is an abstract object that is intended for re-use in other objects, such as components, variables, and parameters. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}